    <item>
      <title>信贷强劲增长今年首次遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/credit-s-strong-run-stumbles-in-first-this-year-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从一项指标来看，全球公司债券本月的表现有望创下自去年年底以来的最差月度表现，这再次引发了有关信贷相对于其他固定收益类别的相对价值的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/credit-s-strong-run-stumbles-in-first-this-year-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 16:31:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
